Evaluating your teacher is something interesting. Each student should have the chance to evaluate his or her teacher once a year.
Evaluating your teacher gives you the feeling that your voice is heard and that your opinion is important to others.
Evaluating the teacher helps also the teacher and the principal of the school.
The evaluation will help the teacher to be better in his weakness points that the student mentioned and also help the principal to choose the suitable class grade for this teacher.
So, evaluating the teacher is very important issue for more than one person or group, it has many benefits that will help us to be better and better.